            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ IN NOMINE DOMINI SALVATORIS NOSTRI IESU CHRISTI DEI ETERNI. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_magnificus #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3022">SECUNDUS IORDANUS</persName> DIVINA ORDINANTE
                        CLEMENTIA CAPUANORUM <rs key="#Princeps">PRINCEPS</rs> PETITIONIBUS
                        DILECTORUM SUORUM BARONUM CLEMENTER AC CLEMENTER FAVET. Nos secundus
                        Iordanus divina ordinante clementia, Capuanorum princeps, notum fieri
                        volumus omnibus fidelibus nostri, quoniam ob salutem et remedium animarum
                        quondam <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs> predecessorum nostrorum,
                            <persName key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Richardi</persName> silicet <rs key="#grandparentOf">avi</rs> et
                            <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs>, et <persName key="#Princeps #siblingOf"
                            ref="#people/3010">Richardi</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Princeps #siblingOf" ref="#people/3019">Robberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">fratrum</rs> omniumque <rs key="#familyOf"
                            >parentum</rs> nostrorum, <rs key="#Mother_churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs><orgName key="#Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3053"> Beati Pauli</orgName> que est mater in
                            <rs key="#Cities">urbe</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000">Aversana</placeName> honorare et
                        exaltare cupientes,<rs key="#Intercessory"> per interventum</rs> quoque
                        domni <persName key="#Intercessory #Bishops #Personal_rank"
                            ref="#people/3039">Robberti</persName> eiusdem ecclesie <rs
                            key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>, precibus etiam nostrorum dilectorum
                        subscriptorum baronum <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3091">Willelmi videlicet de Pirolo</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/3032">Aymonis de
                            Argentia</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3094">Raynaldi Lupini</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/5030">Ihon de
                        Doeli</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/4249"
                            >Hugonis de Fayda</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3078"
                            >Stantionis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vice principis</rs>, predictae aecclesiae
                        Sancti Pauli apostoli, per hoc principale scriptum, in perpetuum, damus, et
                        tradendo confirmamus <rs key="#Churches/religious_bodies">cappellam</rs>
                        nostram <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Levies #Churches/religious_bodies"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3803">Sancte Fidis</orgName> in <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            >palatio</rs> nostro Averse sitam, cum balneo nostro iusta idem palatium
                        constituto, <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">villanis</rs>, <rs key="#Levies"
                            >redditibus</rs>, presis, casis fabricis et infabricis, cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris cultis et incultis</rs>, arbustis et
                        omnibus pertinentiis suis, ad possessionem ac potestatem atque dominationem
                        prephate ecclesie Sancti Pauli apostoli et memorati domni Robberti
                        venerabilis episcopi cunctorumque successorum eius. Remota omni
                        inquietitudine, contrarietate atque molestia omnium principum successorum
                        nostrorum vel vice principum, comitum vel vice comitum, iudicum,
                        sculdahorum, castaldeorum aliorumque omnium mortalium personarum. Quod si
                        quis huius nostrae donationis et traditionis pagine contemptor aut in aliquo
                        violator esse presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">sexcentas libras auri
                            purissimi </rs>persolvat, medietatem nostro sacro palatio et medietatem
                        predicte ecclesie Sancti Pauli apostoli, Aversane sedis, et prephato domno
                        Robberto venerabili episcopo eiusque successoribus. Solutaque pena librarum,
                        hec nostra donatio firma, munita atque inviolabilis maneat in perpetuum. Et
                        ut hoc firmius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur, manu propria
                        illud corroboravimus, et nostri sigilli impressione iussimus insigniri.
                        SIGNUM DOMNI (M) SECUNDI IORDANI <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            >GLORIOSISSIMI</rs> AC <rs key="#Vir_magnificus">MAGNIFICI
                        </rs>PRINCIPIS. Ex iussione prephate serenissime potestatis, scripsi EGO
                            <persName key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3037">PHILIPPUS</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">PALATINUS IUDEX</rs>, in anno dominice incarnationis M. C.
                        XX primo, et primo anno principatus domni Iordani gloriosi principis Capue.
                        Datum in urbe <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000"
                            >Aversana</placeName>, in mense martio, per indictionem quartam decimam.
                        + Ego Willelmus de Pirolo. + Ego Aymon de Argentia. + Ego Raynaldus Lupinus.
                        + Ego Ihon de Doeli + Ego Ugo de Fayda. + Ego Stantio vice princeps. </ab>
